The paper proposes a coding scheme for a MIMO-OFDM system, which falls under the information theory (cs.IT) and networking and internet architecture (cs.NI) categories. The use of reconfigurable antennas also involves system control and optimization (cs.SY). The paper also discusses simulation results, which could fall under multimedia (cs.MM) and computer communication (cs.COM) categories.
